48:10.181 --> 48:11.182
Never hungry.

48:11.933 --> 48:12.892
Born full.

48:14.602 --> 48:15.437
Not us.

48:18.189 --> 48:20.525
The world wasn't built
for guys like us.

48:21.693 --> 48:24.195
That's why we gotta take
whatever we decide is ours.

48:25.238 --> 48:27.949
