what it's like

50:37.871 --> 50:39.039
to get their hands dirty.

50:39.122 --> 50:41.249
That's what they hire
guys like me for,

50:41.332 --> 50:43.501
which means I got direct access
to the ground game.

50:44.044 --> 50:46.880
