51:17.452 --> 51:19.788
But it's my guys
doing all the heavy lifting.

51:19.871 --> 51:21.831
Yeah, revenge don't come easy.

51:23.041 --> 51:24.292
Come on, Sal.

51:25.543 --> 51:27.337
Don't you fucking miss it?

51:29.589 --> 51:30.423
Respect?

51:32.050 --> 51:34.344
That's really what Carmine stole
from you, ain't it?

51:36.096 --> 51:37.472
He was a dirty rat.

51:38.515 --> 51:40.058
