51:40.892 --> 51:42.227
Ain't no changing that.

51:44.354 --> 51:45.355
But he's dead,

51:46.231 --> 51:47.482
and I'm here now,

51:47.565 --> 51:49.526
and I'm offering you
the opportunity of a lifetime.

51:49.609 --> 51:52.028
And this first hit,
it's just the beginning.

51:52.654 --> 51:54.489
I know a lot more
than people think.

51:55.448 --> 51:57.075
I'll keep playing double agent.

51:58.201 --> 51:59.035
You and me,

52:00.495 --> 52:02.080
