right under your nose,

52:28.648 --> 52:30.191
and you got nothing
to do with it?

52:31.401 --> 52:32.485
The fuck outta here.

52:35.780 --> 52:37.907
Look, I can see you're upset.

52:38.533 --> 52:39.784
Trust takes time.

52:40.785 --> 52:42.037
But this ain't bullshit.

52:43.163 --> 52:45.665
Whoever controls Drops
controls the streets.

52:45.749 --> 52:46.875
You know that's right.

52:49.085 --> 52:50.003
So how about this?

52:50.795 --> 52:52.088
I'll come back
in a couple of days...

52:52.172 --> 52:54.507
I never wanna see
your smug face again.

52:54.591 --> 52:56.384
...we'll see
if we can't work something out.

52:57.677 --> 52:59.054
It's good seeing you.
You look good.

52:59.929 --> 53:01.348
-Fuck off.
-Think on it, Sal.

53:05.185 --> 53:06.186
