53:11.608 --> 53:12.776
Ain't this yours?

53:17.447 --> 53:18.782
Where did you get this?

53:18.865 --> 53:20.575
Carmine. Wore it as his own.

53:22.869 --> 53:23.912
The Falcones...

53:25.497 --> 53:27.499
