the spine and...

01:02:21.074 --> 01:02:22.409
All right, all right, all right.

01:02:22.492 --> 01:02:23.660
You know what? It's fine.

01:02:24.285 --> 01:02:25.328
Room to grow.

01:02:25.870 --> 01:02:27.497
