01:03:09.080 --> 01:03:10.957
Yeah. You earned it.

01:03:11.833 --> 01:03:13.877
You know, for the most part.

01:03:14.502 --> 01:03:16.755
And guys like us,
we gotta stick together.

01:03:22.260 --> 01:03:24.095
It's better, right? Come on.

01:03:24.179 --> 01:03:25.347
